1️⃣ Assign the User to the Read-Only Group

Go to Settings → Users & Companies → Users.

Open the user you want to test (e.g., Test User).

Scroll to Access Rights / Groups.

Add the user to the group:

Read-Only User → user_readonly.group_read_only_user


This is the group your module checks in has_group().

2️⃣ Test Stock Quant Creation

Log in as that user.

Go to Inventory → Operations → Products on Hand / Inventory Adjustments.

Try to create a new stock quant / inventory record.

Expected behavior:

Error popup:

The requested operation cannot be completed due to security restrictions.
Please contact your system administrator.


You cannot save the record.

3️⃣ Test Stock Quant Editing

Try to edit an existing stock quant.

Expected behavior: same AccessError.

Normal users (not in the read-only group) should be able to create/edit normally.
